<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Capital Gains Tax Calculator 2025 | MyTaxCalcs</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Free capital gains tax calculator for 2025. Estimate short-term and long-term federal tax on stocks, crypto, real estate, and other asset sales. Includes NIIT.">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta property="og:title" content="Capital Gains Tax Calculator 2025 | MyTaxCalcs">
  <meta property="og:description" content="Estimate your 2025 federal capital gains tax on stocks, crypto, real estate, and other assets. Includes Net Investment Income Tax (NIIT).">
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://mytaxcalcs.com/capital-gains-tax-calculator">
  <meta property="og:type" content="website">
  <meta property="og:site_name" content="MyTaxCalcs">
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary">
  <meta name="twitter:title" content="Capital Gains Tax Calculator 2025 | MyTaxCalcs">
  <meta name="twitter:description" content="Estimate your 2025 federal capital gains tax. Includes NIIT and long-term vs short-term rates.">

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">

  <script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-FS9HCDT0D7"></script>
  <script>window.dataLayer=window.dataLayer||[];function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}gtag('js',new Date());gtag('config','G-FS9HCDT0D7');</script>
  <script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-5193834725888549" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

  <style>
    /* ── BREADCRUMB ── */
    .breadcrumb {
      max-width: 780px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 14px 24px 0;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: #6b7280;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .breadcrumb a { color: #16a34a; text-decoration: none; }
    .breadcrumb a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    .breadcrumb-sep { color: #d1d5db; font-size: 0.75rem; }

    /* ── CALCULATOR LAYOUT ── */
    .calc-page { max-width: 780px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px 60px; }

    .calc-page-header { padding: 28px 0 24px; }
    .calc-page-header .page-eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: #d97706;
      background: #fef3c7;
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 4px 12px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .calc-page-header h1 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.2; margin: 0 0 10px; color: #111827; }
    .calc-page-header p { font-size: 1rem; color: #6b7280; margin: 0; max-width: 580px; }

    /* ── FORM CARD ── */
    .calc-card-form {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    }
    .calc-card-form h2 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111827; margin: 0 0 20px; }

    .form-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; }
    @media (max-width: 580px) { .form-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

    .form-field { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px; }
    .form-field.full { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
    .form-field label { font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 600; color: #374151; }
    .form-field input, .form-field select {
      border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 9px 13px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #111827;
      background: #f9fafb;
      transition: border-color 0.15s;
      width: 100%;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    .form-field input:focus, .form-field select:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: #16a34a;
      background: #fff;
    }

    .form-actions { margin-top: 22px; }
    .btn-calc {
      background: #16a34a;
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 12px 28px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.15s, transform 0.1s;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    .btn-calc:hover { background: #15803d; transform: translateY(-1px); }

    /* ── RESULT CARD ── */
    .result-card {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fdf4 0%, #dcfce7 100%);
      border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 28px 32px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .result-card-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .result-card-header .result-icon {
      width: 38px; height: 38px;
      background: #16a34a;
      border-radius: 10px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    }
    .result-card-header h2 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #14532d; margin: 0; }

    .result-primary {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 20px 24px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: baseline;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .result-primary .result-label { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; color: #6b7280; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
    .result-primary .result-amount { font-size: 2.4rem; font-weight: 800; color: #15803d; }

    .result-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 12px; }
    @media (max-width: 520px) { .result-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

    .result-item {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
    }
    .result-item .ri-label { font-size: 0.78rem; color: #6b7280; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 3px; }
    .result-item .ri-value { font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111827; }
    .result-item .ri-value.positive { color: #16a34a; }
    .result-item .ri-value.warning { color: #d97706; }

    .result-method {
      margin-top: 14px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: #6b7280;
      font-style: italic;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    /* ── AD ZONE ── */
    .ad-zone {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 28px 0;
      min-height: 90px;
    }
    .ad-zone-label {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      color: #9ca3af;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    /* ── HOW IT WORKS ── */
    .hiw-section { margin: 48px 0 0; }
    .section-eyebrow {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: #16a34a;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .hiw-section h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: #111827; margin: 0 0 8px; }
    .hiw-section > p { color: #6b7280; margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 0.95rem; }

    .hiw-steps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .hiw-step {
      display: flex;
      gap: 16px;
      align-items: flex-start;
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 18px 20px;
    }
    .hiw-step-num {
      min-width: 32px; height: 32px;
      background: #f0fdf4;
      border: 2px solid #bbf7d0;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #16a34a;
    }
    .hiw-step-body h3 { font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111827; margin: 0 0 4px; }
    .hiw-step-body p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #6b7280; margin: 0; }

    .formula-box {
      background: #111827;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 20px 24px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      overflow-x: auto;
    }
    .formula-box-label {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      color: #6b7280;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .formula-box code {
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #d1fae5;
      line-height: 1.7;
      display: block;
      white-space: pre;
    }
    .formula-box code .comment { color: #4b5563; }
    .formula-box code .highlight { color: #34d399; }

    /* ── FAQ ── */
    .faq-section { margin: 48px 0 0; }
    .faq-section h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: #111827; margin: 0 0 20px; }

    .faq-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
    .faq-item {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .faq-question {
      width: 100%;
      background: none;
      border: none;
      padding: 17px 20px;
      text-align: left;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #111827;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .faq-question:hover { background: #f9fafb; }
    .faq-chevron {
      min-width: 20px; height: 20px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #f3f4f6;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      transition: transform 0.2s;
    }
    .faq-item.open .faq-chevron { transform: rotate(180deg); background: #dcfce7; }
    .faq-answer {
      display: none;
      padding: 0 20px 17px;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      color: #6b7280;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }
    .faq-item.open .faq-answer { display: block; }

    /* ── RELATED CALCULATORS ── */
    .related-section { margin: 48px 0 0; }
    .related-section h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: #111827; margin: 0 0 16px; }
    .related-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 14px; }
    @media (max-width: 580px) { .related-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }
    @media (max-width: 380px) { .related-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

    .related-card {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 18px 16px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
      transition: border-color 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s, transform 0.15s;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    .related-card:hover {
      border-color: #16a34a;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(22,163,74,0.1);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    .related-card-icon {
      width: 36px; height: 36px;
      border-radius: 9px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }
    .related-card strong { font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111827; }
    .related-card span { font-size: 0.78rem; color: #9ca3af; }

    /* ── DISCLAIMER ── */
    .page-disclaimer {
      margin: 40px 0 0;
      background: #f9fafb;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 16px 20px;
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
    .page-disclaimer svg { color: #9ca3af; min-width: 18px; margin-top: 1px; }
    .page-disclaimer p { font-size: 0.82rem; color: #6b7280; margin: 0; line-height: 1.55; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- ── HEADER ── -->
  <header class="site-header">
    <nav class="nav">
      <a href="/" class="logo">
        <span class="logo-mark">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
            <rect x="1" y="1" width="8" height="8" rx="2" fill="#22c55e"/>
            <rect x="11" y="1" width="8" height="8" rx="2" fill="#22c55e" opacity="0.5"/>
            <rect x="1" y="11" width="8" height="8" rx="2" fill="#22c55e" opacity="0.5"/>
            <rect x="11" y="11" width="8" height="8" rx="2" fill="#22c55e" opacity="0.25"/>
          </svg>
        </span>
        <span>MyTaxCalcs</span>
      </a>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/calculators">Calculators</a>
        <a href="/california-income-tax-calculator">States</a>
        <a href="/about">About</a>
        <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
      </div>
      <a class="nav-cta" href="/income-tax-calculator">Get Started</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <!-- ── BREADCRUMB ── -->
  <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
    <a href="/">Home</a>
    <span class="breadcrumb-sep">&#8250;</span>
    <a href="/calculators">Calculators</a>
    <span class="breadcrumb-sep">&#8250;</span>
    <span>Capital Gains Tax Calculator</span>
  </nav>

  <main>
    <div class="calc-page">

      <!-- ── PAGE HEADER ── -->
      <div class="calc-page-header">
        <div class="page-eyebrow">
          <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><polyline points="22 7 13.5 15.5 8.5 10.5 2 17"/></svg>
          Capital Gains Tax
        </div>
        <h1>Capital Gains Tax Calculator</h1>
        <p>Estimate your 2025 federal capital gains tax on stocks, crypto, real estate, and other asset sales. Includes Net Investment Income Tax (NIIT).</p>
      </div>

      <!-- ── RESULT (shown after POST) ── -->
      <% if (result) { %>
      <div class="result-card">
        <div class="result-card-header">
          <div class="result-icon">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 7 13.5 15.5 8.5 10.5 2 17"/><polyline points="16 7 22 7 22 13"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h2>Your Capital Gains Tax Estimate</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="result-primary">
          <span class="result-label">Total Estimated Tax</span>
          <span class="result-amount">$<%= result.totalEstimatedTax.toLocaleString('en-US', {minimumFractionDigits: 2, maximumFractionDigits: 2}) %></span>
        </div>

        <div class="result-grid">
          <div class="result-item">
            <div class="ri-label">Net Capital Gain</div>
            <div class="ri-value">$<%= result.netGain.toLocaleString('en-US', {minimumFractionDigits: 2, maximumFractionDigits: 2}) %></div>
          </div>
          <div class="result-item">
            <div class="ri-label">Adjusted Basis</div>
            <div class="ri-value">$<%= result.adjustedBasis.toLocaleString('en-US', {minimumFractionDigits: 2, maximumFractionDigits: 2}) %></div>
          </div>
          <div class="result-item">
            <div class="ri-label">Capital Gains Tax</div>
            <div class="ri-value warning">$<%= result.estimatedCapitalGainsTax.toLocaleString('en-US', {minimumFractionDigits: 2, maximumFractionDigits: 2}) %></div>
          </div>
          <div class="result-item">
            <div class="ri-label">Net Investment Income Tax (3.8%)</div>
            <div class="ri-value warning">$<%= result.estimatedNIIT.toLocaleString('en-US', {minimumFractionDigits: 2, maximumFractionDigits: 2}) %></div>
          </div>
          <div class="result-item">
            <div class="ri-label">Effective Gains Rate</div>
            <div class="ri-value"><%= (result.effectiveCapitalGainsRate * 100).toFixed(2) %>%</div>
          </div>
          <div class="result-item">
            <div class="ri-label">Holding Period</div>
            <div class="ri-value positive"><%= result.holdingPeriod === 'long' ? 'Long-term' : 'Short-term' %></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="result-method"><%= result.taxMethod %></div>
      </div>

      <!-- ── LEADERBOARD AD (after results) ── -->
      <div class="ad-zone">
        <div class="ad-zone-label">Advertisement</div>
        <ins class="adsbygoogle"
          style="display:block"
          data-ad-client="ca-pub-5193834725888549"
          data-ad-slot="5205436277"
          data-ad-format="auto"
          data-full-width-responsive="true"></ins>
        <script>(adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});</script>
      </div>

      <% } %>

      <!-- ── CALCULATOR FORM ── -->
      <div class="calc-card-form">
        <h2>Enter Your Details</h2>
        <form method="POST" action="/capital-gains-tax-calculator">
          <div class="form-grid">

            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="salePrice">Sale Price ($)</label>
              <input type="number" id="salePrice" name="salePrice" min="0" step="any"
                value="<%= form.salePrice || '' %>" placeholder="e.g. 250000" required>
            </div>

            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="purchasePrice">Original Purchase Price ($)</label>
              <input type="number" id="purchasePrice" name="purchasePrice" min="0" step="any"
                value="<%= form.purchasePrice || '' %>" placeholder="e.g. 150000" required>
            </div>

            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="improvements">Improvements Added ($)</label>
              <input type="number" id="improvements" name="improvements" min="0" step="any"
                value="<%= form.improvements || '' %>" placeholder="e.g. 15000">
            </div>

            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="sellingCosts">Selling Costs ($)</label>
              <input type="number" id="sellingCosts" name="sellingCosts" min="0" step="any"
                value="<%= form.sellingCosts || '' %>" placeholder="e.g. 5000">
            </div>

            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="capitalLosses">Capital Loss Carryover ($)</label>
              <input type="number" id="capitalLosses" name="capitalLosses" min="0" step="any"
                value="<%= form.capitalLosses || '' %>" placeholder="e.g. 0">
            </div>

            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="otherTaxableIncome">Other Taxable Income ($)</label>
              <input type="number" id="otherTaxableIncome" name="otherTaxableIncome" min="0" step="any"
                value="<%= form.otherTaxableIncome || '' %>" placeholder="e.g. 75000" required>
            </div>

            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="filingStatus">Filing Status</label>
              <select id="filingStatus" name="filingStatus">
                <option value="single" <%= (form.filingStatus === 'single' || !form.filingStatus) ? 'selected' : '' %>>Single</option>
                <option value="marriedJoint" <%= form.filingStatus === 'marriedJoint' ? 'selected' : '' %>>Married Filing Jointly</option>
                <option value="marriedSeparate" <%= form.filingStatus === 'marriedSeparate' ? 'selected' : '' %>>Married Filing Separately</option>
                <option value="headHousehold" <%= form.filingStatus === 'headHousehold' ? 'selected' : '' %>>Head of Household</option>
              </select>
            </div>

            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="holdingPeriod">Holding Period</label>
              <select id="holdingPeriod" name="holdingPeriod">
                <option value="long" <%= (form.holdingPeriod === 'long' || !form.holdingPeriod) ? 'selected' : '' %>>Long-term (held over 1 year)</option>
                <option value="short" <%= form.holdingPeriod === 'short' ? 'selected' : '' %>>Short-term (held 1 year or less)</option>
              </select>
            </div>

          </div>
          <div class="form-actions">
            <button type="submit" class="btn-calc">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 7 13.5 15.5 8.5 10.5 2 17"/></svg>
              Calculate Capital Gains Tax
            </button>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>

      <!-- ── HOW IT WORKS ── -->
      <div class="hiw-section">
        <div class="section-eyebrow">How It Works</div>
        <h2>How Capital Gains Tax Is Calculated</h2>
        <p>Your tax depends on how long you held the asset and your total income. Here is the step-by-step process we use.</p>

        <div class="hiw-steps">
          <div class="hiw-step">
            <div class="hiw-step-num">1</div>
            <div class="hiw-step-body">
              <h3>Calculate Adjusted Basis</h3>
              <p>Start with your original purchase price, then add the cost of any improvements and selling expenses. This is your adjusted basis.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="hiw-step">
            <div class="hiw-step-num">2</div>
            <div class="hiw-step-body">
              <h3>Find Your Net Capital Gain</h3>
              <p>Subtract the adjusted basis from your sale price to get the gross gain. Then subtract any capital loss carryover to get the net gain.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="hiw-step">
            <div class="hiw-step-num">3</div>
            <div class="hiw-step-body">
              <h3>Apply the Right Tax Rate</h3>
              <p>Long-term gains (held over 1 year) use preferential 0%, 15%, or 20% rates. Short-term gains are taxed as ordinary income using your marginal bracket.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="hiw-step">
            <div class="hiw-step-num">4</div>
            <div class="hiw-step-body">
              <h3>Add Net Investment Income Tax</h3>
              <p>High earners may owe an additional 3.8% NIIT on the lesser of net investment income or the amount by which MAGI exceeds the threshold for your filing status.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="formula-box">
          <div class="formula-box-label">Formula Reference</div>
          <code><span class="comment">// Step 1: Adjusted Basis</span>
<span class="highlight">Adjusted Basis</span>  = Purchase Price + Improvements + Selling Costs

<span class="comment">// Step 2: Net Gain</span>
<span class="highlight">Gross Gain</span>       = Sale Price - Adjusted Basis
<span class="highlight">Net Gain</span>         = Gross Gain - Capital Loss Carryover

<span class="comment">// Step 3: Long-term rates (2025, Single filer)</span>
0%  rate applies up to $48,350 of taxable income
15% rate applies from $48,350 to $533,400
20% rate applies above $533,400

<span class="comment">// Step 4: Net Investment Income Tax</span>
<span class="highlight">NIIT (3.8%)</span>      = min(Net Gain, max(MAGI - Threshold, 0))</code>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ── MID-PAGE AD ── -->
      <div class="ad-zone">
        <div class="ad-zone-label">Advertisement</div>
        <ins class="adsbygoogle"
          style="display:block"
          data-ad-client="ca-pub-5193834725888549"
          data-ad-slot="4212978293"
          data-ad-format="auto"
          data-full-width-responsive="true"></ins>
